    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was in Wroclaw a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I joined a-- that was called the Kibbutz Mizrahi, was-- were with my friends.",
